text: Kyle Carter (born 8 January 1969) is a Canadian equestrian. He competed in two events at the 2008 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1969 births Category:Living people Category:Canadian male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Canada Category:Equestrians at the 2008 Summer Olympics Category:Pan American Games medalists in equestrian Category:Pan American Games silver medalists for Canada Category:Equestrians at the 2007 Pan American Games Category:Sportspeople from Calgary
